description: The Grunt hook from Sails core in v1.0 and up.
name: sails-hook-grunt

scripts.custom-tests: node ./node_modules/mocha/bin/mocha && echo "Custom tests all passed." && echo
scripts.lint: node ./node_modules/eslint/bin/eslint . --max-warnings=0 && echo '✔  Your code looks good.'
scripts.test: npm run lint && npm run custom-tests
